data.description: Enjoy stunning wrap around views of the ocean, mountains and city from this 33rd floor corner unit apartment! Regency Tower offers low maintenance fees and is centrally located minutes from Waikiki, Ala Moana and the University of Hawaii. Features include a washer dryer in the unit, an open floor plan and cool trade wind breezes. Amenities include security guard, secured entry, lots of guest parking, bbq, pool and convenience store.
